Sentencas: The composite perovskites are promising low/intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cell (LT/IT-SOFC) cathode materials, which can combine the complementary advantages of multi-components.
Titulo: Comparison of nanostructured composite cathodes synthesized by liquid self-assembly and nanosolid mechanical-mixing for solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: Here, novel liquid self-assembly (SA) is compared with nanosolid mechanical-mixing (MM) for the high-performance nanostructured composite.
Titulo: Comparison of nanostructured composite cathodes synthesized by liquid self-assembly and nanosolid mechanical-mixing for solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The same composition of the active BaCo0.96Zr0.04O2.6-delta (12hBC, 38 mol%) with the stable BaZr0.82Co0.18O3-delta (BZC, 62 mol%) is designed to compare the effects of different syntheses on composite properties.
Titulo: Comparison of nanostructured composite cathodes synthesized by liquid self-assembly and nanosolid mechanical-mixing for solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The BZC-12hBC (SA) can achieve molecular-level contact of multiple phases, which exhibits superior electrical conductivity, surface and heterointerface activity to those of BZC-12hBC (MM).
Titulo: Comparison of nanostructured composite cathodes synthesized by liquid self-assembly and nanosolid mechanical-mixing for solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: When further applied on LT/IT-SOFC, the cell with BZC-12hBC (SA) cathode achieves the remarkable peak power densities of 2.06-.24 W cm(-2) at 700 -500 degrees C, while the cell with BZC-12hBC (MM) cathode only exhibits 0.63-0.11 W cm(-2).
Titulo: Comparison of nanostructured composite cathodes synthesized by liquid self-assembly and nanosolid mechanical-mixing for solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The electrochemical analysis reveals that BZC-12hBC (SA) cathode possesses better oxygen dissociative adsorption and species transportation than those of the BZC-12hBC (MM) cathode.
Titulo: Comparison of nanostructured composite cathodes synthesized by liquid self-assembly and nanosolid mechanical-mixing for solid oxide fuel cell
